history.content:
Don't take 4 technicals in one semester unless you've had success in the past with this kind of schedule. I suggest dropping one of them and replacing it with an easy or easier class. 

CS 189 is pretty hard and does take a lot of time unless you've had significant previous experience.

Any suggestions whether or not it’s a good idea to take these 4 classes in the same semester and the relevant workload of each classes compared to the ones that I’ve taken?
